<section anchor="cffmt"><name>cffmt</name>

<section anchor="name"><name>Name</name>
<t>cffmt - CFEngine pretty printer/formatter</t>
</section>

<section anchor="synopsis"><name>Synopsis</name>
<t>cffmt` <em>[OPTION]</em>... <em>[FILE]</em></t>
</section>

<section anchor="description"><name>Description</name>
<t>Cffmt will take a CFengine file out of <strong>FILE</strong> or from standard input and will reformat it.</t>
<t>Options are:</t>

<dl spacing="compact">
<dt><tt>-a</tt></dt>
<dd>print the AST to standard error</dd>
<dt><tt>-p</tt></dt>
<dd>print the pretty printed document to standard output (defaults to true)</dd>
<dt><tt>-l</tt></dt>
<dd>show lexer tokens</dd>
<dt><tt>-f</tt></dt>
<dd>if parsing fails only show the name of the file being parsed.</dd>
</dl>
</section>

